{"tid":1681328,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[榮光歸港人互助計劃] 讓有需要既手足都能以成本價買野","createTime":"2019-10-29T10:49:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T12:32:54.000Z","uid":287547,"like":34,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"308680aa2a80ee8d2f2257b47120459adb2cbf1b","tid":1681328,"uid":287547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:49:44.000Z","msg":"計劃名稱: <strong>榮光歸港人互助計劃</strong><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n前言:<br />\n<br />\n出發點是眼見好多手足因為發夢, 因為買文具, 因為與家人不和等等原因而收入不繼, 甚至於連三餐都食唔飽. <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以好希望可以改善有需要既手足既生活, 除左捐錢捐文具俾我地既手足，<br />\n更加希望可以減低手足的生活成本, 所以試行呢個計劃。<br />\n如果成功試行, 希望有更多手足能推出更多商店分佈係各行各業。<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">營業模式:</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n根據手足經濟能力的不同:<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<span style=\"color: red;\">經濟能力充裕</span> ----&gt; 以 <strong>正常價格</strong> 購買貨品 ----&gt; 令店鋪能持續經營 ----&gt; 擴充并聘請義士 + 利潤支持長期抗爭<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<span style=\"color: red;\">手足有需要幫手</span> ----&gt; 利用優惠碼以 <strong>成本價</strong> 購買貨品<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">(注1)</span>&nbsp;----&gt; 手足減輕生活成本 ----&gt; 可支配收入增加 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">注1 : 利用優惠碼以成本價購買貨品示範圖</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iFFkaSY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiFFkaSY.png&h=84f87ba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n構想:<br />\n<br />\n暫時定位為 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">實驗性質企業</span></span>, 首階段將會試行一個月研究其可行性, 若確切可行, 將會公佈計劃的財務相關報表, 及解答大家的疑問.希望能更為普及, 各行業都有類似企業出現.<br />\n<br />\n量變成質變, 若大量類似模式企業係各行各業出現, 將能一方面很大程度上減輕有需要手足們的生活成本, 而且能擴大真香港人經濟圈, 長期抗爭.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n實驗企業名稱 : <strong>有得揀</strong><br />\n營業形式 : <strong>網店</strong><br />\n網店地址 : <a href=\"http://www.unitchoice.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.unitchoice.com&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg6Cfq%2BeyIt6E%2B7HnZU0UyvE%3D&h=370115e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.unitchoice.com</a><br />\n商品種類 : 電子及手機配件<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n本項目的網店製作及商業登記等步驟已完成, 正在新增商品中. 預計會於11月中旬開業.<br />\n<br />\n優惠碼及項目詳情將於Telegram channel 及 Facebook專頁公佈<br />\n<br />\nTelegram channel : <a href=\"https://t.me/glorytohkpplplan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fglorytohkpplplan&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg6Cfq%2BeyIt6E%2B7HnZU0UyvE%3D&h=c98409d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/glorytohkpplplan</a><br />\n<br />\nFacebook page: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/unitChoice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FunitChoice&d=WC8zRIkQRph3x4hQUB%2Bsg6Cfq%2BeyIt6E%2B7HnZU0UyvE%3D&h=bf456898\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/unitChoice</a><br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n請各手足多多支持, 幫手推一推, &nbsp;P牌推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97ebda431dcb5a3a7ba0daf286066e2079fe2c3e","tid":1681328,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:50:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zyBfyPB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzyBfyPB.jpg&h=2708f4ca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Mtm3RDU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMtm3RDU.jpg&h=fd9c9c47&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"a993f47fe9fe84f16005cba6238e8259b3642c36","tid":1681328,"uid":285371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:51:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3725fe501f118271ed6e9b36ffdaf7a8d2e10a20","tid":1681328,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T10:51:38.000Z","msg":"同你地講，俾把機關槍我，我可以一個人由香港一路殺上北京<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1681326\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1681326</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"29dc01e5548d